internal=em1
set skip on lo
block drop log
pass out on egress nat-to (egress) keep state
pass in on egress proto tcp from any to egress port ssh keep state
pass in on $internal proto udp from 0.0.0.0 port 68 to 255.255.255.255 port 67 keep state
pass in on $internal proto udp from ($internal:network) to ($internal) port domain rdr-to 127.0.0.1 keep state
pass in on $internal from ($internal:network) to !($internal:network) keep state
